# 懵然不知
(pos:成語)
<explanation>
yue:完全唔知發生咩事，或者對某件事完全冇概念（量詞：個）
eng:completely unaware; in the dark about something
<eg>
yue:佢成日懵然不知，連自己點解被炒魷魚都唔明。 (keoi5 sing4 jat6 mung5 jin4 bat1 zi1, lin4 zi6 gei2 dim2 gaak3 bei6 caau2 jau5 jyu5 dou1 mung4 ming4.)
eng:He was completely unaware and didn't even understand why he got fired. [end of text]


